net.sourceforge.nite.search.rewriter

Class SubqueryTemplate

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.sourceforge.nite.search.rewriter.SubqueryTemplate

  • public class SubqueryTemplate
extends java.lang.Object
    A class recording the information which will eventually be used to create a subquery Node for the new query. Merely records a list of the variables which must be declared, along with a list of the conditions which should be evaluated.
